createJavaObjects

public java.util.List createJavaObjects(Document document,
                                        java.util.List<CellParseError> parseErrors)
Creates a list of java objects. For this method to work, the lineType attribute of each line have to contain the full class name of the class to create for each line. Also the set method for each attribute have to match exactly to the name of each cell.

Parameters:
document -
Returns:
A list of Java objects.
